				<wikidot:authorName>Vicious_Unicycle</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5872098</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You had me at &quot;[picture of a grand piano] in its solid state.&quot;</p> <p>That said, I do think there's a slight inconsistency in referring to people who have injected enough piano juice to turn anomalous as &quot;SCP-4394-A subjects&quot; yet referring to the only discussed person who fits that description as -B.</p> <p>But even so, it's short, sweet, and to the point. I like it!</p> 
				 	]]>
